## Amazon Revenue PHP Class
========================

### Installation
```
$ git clone git://github.com/SeoFood/amazon-revenue.git
$ php -r "eval('?>'.file_get_contents('https://getcomposer.org/installer'));"
$ composer update
```
### Update
```
$ git fetch && composer update
```
